SimulationType                MonteCarlo
NumberOfCycles                1
NumberOfInitializationCycles  1
PrintEvery                    1000
PrintPropertiesEvery          1000
Forcefield                    local
ChargeMethod                  Ewald
EwaldPrecision                1e-6
Restart File                  no
CutOff                        {cutoff:.2f}

Framework 0 
            FrameworkName                 simulation
            RemoveAtomNumberCodeFromLabel no
            UseChargesFromCIFFile            yes
            UnitCells                     {na:d} {nb:d} {nc:d}
            ExternalTemperature           313.0
            ExternalPressure              1e4 1e5
	    Movies                        No
	
Component 0 MoleculeName                  CO2
            MoleculeDefinition            local
            TranslationProbability        0.5
            RotationProbability           0.5
            ReinsertionProbability        0.5
            SwapProbability               1.0
	    CreateNumberOfMolecules       0
            MolFraction                   0.198
         
Component 1 MoleculeName                  SO2
            MoleculeDefinition            local
            TranslationProbability        0.5
            RotationProbability           0.5
            ReinsertionProbability        0.5
            SwapProbability               1.0
	    CreateNumberOfMolecules       0
            MolFraction                   0.002
         
Component 2 MoleculeName                  N2
            MoleculeDefinition            local
            TranslationProbability        0.5
            RotationProbability           0.5
            ReinsertionProbability        0.5
            SwapProbability               1.0
	    CreateNumberOfMolecules       0
            MolFraction                   0.8
